{"tid":825971,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[原POST已DEL倒數5日]中環裙掛舖免費試著 專業攝影師註場","createTime":"2018-09-18T02:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T11:50:46.000Z","uid":2772,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5090e07d32b287eb5c0eb1e3cd3d829d4079c08f","tid":825971,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:18:59.000Z","msg":"中環某裙掛舖<br />\n9月23號會有開放日<br />\n<br />\n早幾日上黎搵免費MODEL試著垃圾裙掛俾人屌到七彩<br />\n幾近釀成關公災難之際<br />\n唔知用咩方法洗橫手叫admin bam左佢<br />\npost都冇撚埋<br />\n<br />\n不過咪以為刪左post就得架<br />\n當日咁撚臭串<br />\n而家又幫你開返<br />\n<br />\n早幾日佢地招免費MODEL試著一世人只可以著一次既裙掛<br />\n<br />\n佢地有專業攝影師註場(唔知係咪又係免費請返黎)<br />\n如果自己預左唔會嫁得出<br />\n一世人都唔會有機會著到一次裙掛<br />\n又或者唔怕翻頭嫁既話<br />\n不妨一試<br />\n<br />\n仲聲稱豬扒都得<br />\n有冇篩選就你諗你<br />\n<br />\n唔洗錢可以試著<br />\n仲可以自己化妝<br />\n唔洗你屈就佢D化妝師<br />\n幾撚偉大呀<br />\n<br />\n當日佢留既電話係<br />\n蕭小姐98019606<br />\n<br />\n有關蕭小姐既電話亦可以係<a href=\"http://sweetaunt.com/搵到\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsweetaunt.com%2F%E6%90%B5%E5%88%B0&d=57EJI2h5IKG69o9%2FHbVeI3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ed1aea5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sweetaunt.com/搵到</a>"},{"pid":"4b0cacf49aec0f7a7fa51746465807716e852ff9","tid":825971,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:23:15.000Z","msg":"原post在此 LMGTFY<br />\n第一個result就係<br />\n<br />\n裙褂店免費試玩以及徵求免費私影MODEL | LIHKG 討論區 - <a href=\"http://LIHKG.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">LIHKG.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bfy.tw/Jvys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbfy.tw%2FJvys&d=57EJI2h5IKG69o9%2FHbVeI3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=bbca381c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bfy.tw/Jvys</a>"},{"pid":"f602442ad796eb43d78c9188f276a9b1e45d639d","tid":825971,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19cdc0f996f0928a15ae54f304590666a1a42a44","tid":825971,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":